  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p541550/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/803e3a24ad1340c6af86f3da18c4e68f.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>《王牌播音员2》Anchorman: The Legend Continues</strong><br />\n\t导演：亚当&middot;麦凯 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n\t编剧：威尔&middot;法瑞尔/亚当&middot;麦凯<br />\n\t主演：保罗&middot;路德/威尔&middot;法瑞尔/史蒂夫&middot;卡瑞尔<br />\n\t影片类型：喜剧&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n\t上映时间：2013年12月20日（美国）&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>预告片：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>剧情简介：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t好莱坞喜剧《王牌播报员2》虽然筹拍过程颇为坎坷，但好莱坞&ldquo;烂仔帮&rdquo;的很多成员都回归出演，除了威尔&middot;法瑞尔、保罗&middot;路德、史蒂夫&middot;卡瑞尔之外，《伴娘》女主角克里斯汀&middot;韦格也倾情出演。本片前作《王牌播音员》讲述的是上世纪70年代电视台里一群男播音员与一位美女主播欢乐相斗的故事,而精彩还在继续。The making process of the Hollywood comedy &quot;Anchorman 2：The Legend Continues&quot; is full of&nbsp;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/frustration\" target=\"_blank\">frustrations</a>, but many members of Hollywood &quot;Frat Pack&quot; have back in.In addition to Will Ferrell, Paul Rudd, Steve Carell, the &quot;Bridesmaid&quot; actress Kristen Wiig also plays. The film &quot;Anchorman&quot; tells the story of the last century 70's TV station of a group of male <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/announcer\" target=\"_blank\">announcer</a> with a beautiful woman anchor, and the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/legand\" target=\"_blank\">legand</a> will continue.</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p541550/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p541550\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/